---
title: Sweet and Savoury Sesame Shrimp with Broccoli and Sweet Bell Pepper
description: Succulent shrimp get a quick toss in a sweet soy chili sauce with the alluring aroma of sesame oil. Tender-crisp broccoli and sweet bell pepper give the perfect crunch to this snappy dish. You will not miss take-out with this one!

